Es un error de nuestro trabajo.

00:17:35.790 --> 00:17:37.630
No expliqué bien la demanda.

00:17:37.790 --> 00:17:39.390
Pero es realmente urgente.

00:17:41.950 --> 00:17:42.550
Bien.

00:17:42.830 --> 00:17:43.710
Gracias.

00:17:49.590 --> 00:17:50.350
Listo.

00:17:50.990 --> 00:17:52.150
Sea como sea,

00:17:52.150 --> 00:17:54.680
